==English==

===Noun===

{{en-noun|Albarelli}}

A [[ceramic]] [[pharmacy]] or drug jar, generally [[majolica]] ware. They are usually tall rather than wide, and often of a [[waist]]ed shape. Albarelli originated in the [[Middle East]] but their name is from Italian.

